### Billing - Get available plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/plan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Billing - Start Starter checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "starter"
}

###

### Billing - Start Pro checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "pro"
}

###

### Billing - Start legend checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "legend"
}

###

### Billing - Invalid plan (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "gold"
}

###

### Billing - Callback (successful payment)
# Replace TEST_REFERENCE with a real Paystack transaction reference.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/callback?reference=4e940835-c8b9-494d-a05f-c05843730fbe-starter-29740312

###

### Billing - Callback (missing reference)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/callback

###

### Billing - Webhook (testing only)
# NOTE:
# This request will FAIL signature verification unless you generate a valid
# x-paystack-signature using your PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY.
#
# For local development you can temporarily bypass signature verification
# if needed.

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
x-paystack-signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "event": "charge.success",
  "data": {
    "reference": "test_reference",
    "metadata": {
      "userId": "4e940835-c8b9-494d-a05f-c05843730fbe",
      "tier": "pro"
    }
  }
}